doctor.name: Dr. Mohsina Haider
doctor.info: Dr. Mohsina Haider is a Gynecologist in Kushtia. Her qualification is MBBS (DMC), MCPS, FCPS (OBGYN). She is a Consultant, Gynecology & Obstetrics at 250 Bedded General Hospital, Kushtia. She regularly provides treatment to her patients at Sono Consultation Center, Kushtia. Practicing hour of Dr. Mohsina Haider at Sono Consultation Center, Kushtia is 3pm to 8pm (Sat to Thu), 10am to 12.30pm (Fri).

chamber.address: Sono Tower 2, Court Para, Kushtia, Bangladesh
